[src:wavelet-transform/haar-wavelet] Usually one separates the sequences *s* and *d* and continues with transforming the sequence *s*.
[src:wavelet-transform/haar-wavelet] Sequence *s* is often referred to as the *averages* part, whereas *d* is known as the *details* part.
